<h1>WebSocket Demo (Rails 7 + Stimulus)</h1>

<div data-controller="ping">
  <p>Status: <strong data-ping-target="status" style="color: orange;">Connecting...</strong></p>
  <p>Listening for messages on <code>PingChannel</code>...</p>

  <div data-ping-target="messages" style="border: 1px solid #ccc; padding: 10px; min-height: 100px; margin-top: 10px; background: #f9f9f9;">
  </div>

  <hr>

  <h3>Trigger a message</h3>
  <pre>curl -X POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/pings/dispatch_websocket -d "message=Hello from Stimulus!"</pre>
</div>
